name: Babylonia
description:
Greetings, this is my very first model to release here, I hope you like it.

To use this model, I suggest generating with a resolution of 512X768, DPM++ 2M Karras sampler, and Sampling steps of 20-25, then upscale to 1.5X, and Latent (bicubic antialiased) upscale and Denoising strength of 0.6 with high-res steps of 10, to save time. (set high-res steps to 0 if you want better quality)

Imperlia, a model that is better at clothing, not as exposed as Emperia (WIP) does, and less NSFW.
The final name will be Babylonia

I hope you have fun using my model
